    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the way u phrased that \"essential for a fairer society\" part sounds like a specific policy goal rather than just an economic prediction. can u explain why the shift from capital to labor is considered the \"essential\" way to handle it, vs just focusing on pure GDP growth?",
